ygData.messageBody:
Congrats Tyria! wtg! I musta missed it on your previous post - just caught
my eye.

My little wizzie is just 31. Made a bub off lake Rathe Stone skellys last
night with a group of friends - not solo. It's fun to play a different
class and hard to learn to stand still while casting - heh. And the other
day, while looking thru the old bank vault, I discovered some spell scrolls
that I had forgotten to scribe. Oppsie. One is really nice DD spell too -
heh, guess I am not as "serious" with my wizard.

Sylly
